      Subclasses of Account in account 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Checking
      This class represents a checking account
      Checking accounts have a monthly fee of 25, a minimum balance of 1500 or direct deposit to waive the fee, and an annual interest rate of .05%
      class  MoneyMarket
      This class represents a money market account
      Checking accounts have a monthly fee of 6, a minimum balance of 2500 unless the withdrawals has surpassed 6, and an annual interest rate of .65%
      class  Savings
      This class represents a savings account
      Checking accounts have a monthly fee of 5, a minimum balance of 300 to waive the fee, and an annual interest rate of .25%
      the annual interest rate is .35% on loyal accounts
